@Smart_Contract_HostAddress = http://localhost:5258

### =====================
### SAÚDE
### =====================

### Verificar disponibilidade do servidor gRPC conectado
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/grpc/health
Accept: application/json

### =====================
### GRAFOS
### =====================

### Criar um novo grafo remoto
POST {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "graphId": "contacts-main",
    "graphType": 1,
    "description": "Grafo principal de contatos"
}

### Listar todos os grafos
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs
Accept: application/json

### Obter detalhes de um grafo
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/contacts-main
Accept: application/json

### Verificar integridade de um grafo
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/contacts-main/verify
Accept: application/json

### Validar todos os grafos
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/validate/all
Accept: application/json

### =====================
### BLOCOS / CONTATOS
### =====================

### Adicionar um contato (bloco) ao grafo remoto
POST {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/contacts-main/blocks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "contact": {
        "name": "João Silva",
        "email": "joao.silva@email.com",
        "phone": "+55 11 99999-9999"
    },
    "crossReferences": []
}

### Adicionar outro contato
POST {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/contacts-main/blocks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "contact": {
        "name": "Maria Santos",
        "email": "maria.santos@email.com",
        "phone": "+55 21 88888-8888"
    },
    "crossReferences": []
}

### Obter o último bloco
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/contacts-main/blocks/latest
Accept: application/json

### Obter blocos por range (altura 0 a 5)
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/contacts-main/blocks/range?startHeight=0&endHeight=5
Accept: application/json

### Obter um bloco específico
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/contacts-main/blocks/{hash}
Accept: application/json

### Listar todos os contatos registrados
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/contacts-main/contacts
Accept: application/json

### Obter um contato específico a partir do hash do bloco
GET {{Smart_Contract_HostAddress}}/api/graphs/contacts-main/contacts/{hash}
Accept: application/json

